<view class="page"><text class="page-title">数据字典</text><text class="page-subtitle">由 utils/seed.js 集中维护，离线可用</text><view class="dict-stats"><view wx:for="{{dictionaries}}" wx:key="key" class="metric"><text class="metric-number">{{item.items.length}}</text><text class="metric-label">{{item.name}}</text></view></view><view class="section"><view wx:for="{{dictionaries}}" wx:key="key" class="card dict-card"><view class="row between gap"><view><text class="list-title">{{item.name}}</text><view class="list-subtitle">{{item.model}} · {{item.field}}</view></view><text class="tag success">{{item.items.length}} 项</text></view><view class="divider"></view><view wx:for="{{item.items}}" wx:for-item="option" wx:key="value" class="dict-row"><text class="dict-code">{{option.value}}</text><text>{{option.label}}</text></view><view class="dict-source">utils/seed.js · {{item.key}}</view></view></view><view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="loading" aria-role="status">正在加载字典…</view><view class="notice">新增或修改字典项时，请同步更新 utils/seed.js；在“更多管理”中恢复初始数据后即可重新载入。</view></view>
